<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>The Best Time to Act Is Now</title>
    <style>
      body,
      table,
      td,
      p,
      a {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body {
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      img {
        border: 0;
        display: block;
        outline: none;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        padding: 30px 0;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #1a2744;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-header img {
        max-width: 200px;
        height: auto;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .hero-banner {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2744 0%, #2c4a7c 100%);
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-banner h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.3;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .hero-banner p {
        color: #b8c9e0;
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 36px 40px;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .email-body p {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #444444;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1a2744;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .highlight-box {
        background-color: #f0f5fb;
        border-left: 4px solid #2c4a7c;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 20px 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .highlight-box p {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .highlight-box p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .highlight-box strong {
        color: #1a2744;
      }
      .warning-box {
        background-color: #fef2f2;
        border-left: 4px solid #c53030;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 18px 22px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .warning-box p {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #742a2a;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .warning-box p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .cta-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #2c4a7c;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 36px;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }
      .divider {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #e8ecf1;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .step-item {
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #444;
      }
      .email-footer {
        background-color: #1a2744;
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-footer p {
        color: #8fa3bf;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .email-footer a {
        color: #b8c9e0;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .footer-phone {
        font-size: 16px !important;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 12px !important;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
        .email-body,
        .email-header,
        .hero-banner,
        .email-footer {
          padding-left: 24px !important;
          padding-right: 24px !important;
        }
        .hero-banner h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <table
        class="email-container"
        role="presentation"
        cellpadding="0"
        cellspacing="0"
        width="100%"
      >

        <tr>
          <td class="email-header">
            <img src="cid:emailLogo" alt="Wynn Tax Solutions" />
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td class="hero-banner">
            <h1>Tax Issues Don't Resolve Themselves &mdash;<br />But We Can Help
              Resolve Yours</h1>
            <p>Why taking action sooner protects you more than waiting</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td class="email-body">

            <p class="greeting">Hi {{name}},</p>

            <p>
              We've been in touch a few times now, and we want you to know
              &mdash; whenever you're ready, we're here. There's no pressure and
              no expiration on our willingness to help. But we also want to be
              upfront about something our clients wish they'd known sooner:
              <strong>when it comes to tax issues, time is rarely on your side.</strong>
            </p>

            <div class="warning-box">
              <p><strong>What can happen when tax issues go unaddressed:</strong></p>
              <p>&#10060; Penalties and interest continue to compound daily</p>
              <p>&#10060; The IRS or state agencies may escalate collection
                activity</p>
              <p>&#10060; Certain relief programs have eligibility windows that
                can close</p>
              <p>&#10060; Unfiled returns can trigger automatic assessments that
                overstate what you owe</p>
            </div>

            <p>
              We're not sharing this to alarm you &mdash; we're sharing it
              because we've seen how much better outcomes tend to be when
              clients engage early rather than waiting until enforcement has
              already started. The sooner you have a professional in your
              corner, the more options are typically available to you.
            </p>

            <hr class="divider" />

            <p
              style="font-weight:600; color:#1a2744; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:16px;"
            >
              What acting now looks like
            </p>

            <div class="step-item">
              <strong>1.</strong>
              &nbsp; A 15&ndash;20 minute phone conversation with one of our
              consultants &mdash; free and confidential.
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
              <strong>2.</strong>
              &nbsp; We review where things stand and identify which programs or
              strategies apply to your situation.
            </div>
            <div class="step-item">
              <strong>3.</strong>
              &nbsp; You walk away with a clear understanding of your options
              &mdash; whether or not you decide to move forward with us.
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box">
              <p><strong>There's genuinely no downside to a conversation.</strong></p>
              <p>
                Our consultation is complimentary. You'll get honest answers
                about where you stand, what your options are, and what the
                realistic timeline looks like. Many clients tell us the hardest
                part was making the first call &mdash; and that everything felt
                easier after that.
              </p>
            </div>

            <p>
              We've helped thousands of people move past their tax problems and
              get back to focusing on their lives and businesses. We'd like the
              chance to do the same for you.
            </p>

            <div class="cta-wrapper">
              <a href="{{scheduleUrl}}" class="cta-button">Schedule Your Free
                Consultation Now</a>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align:center; font-size:14px; color:#666;">
              Or call us toll-free:
              <strong style="color:#1a2744;">866-770-3749</strong>
            </p>

            <hr class="divider" />

            <p style="font-size:13px; color:#888; line-height:1.6;">
              You're receiving this email because you recently expressed
              interest in Wynn Tax Solutions. We'll continue to check in
              periodically, but if you'd prefer not to hear from us, simply
              reply and let us know.
            </p>

          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td class="email-footer">
            <p class="footer-phone">&#128222; 866-770-3749</p>
            <p><strong style="color:#fff;">Wynn Tax Solutions</strong></p>
            <p>Tax Resolution &amp; Relief Services</p>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;">
              <a
                href="https://www.wynntaxsolutions.com"
              >wynntaxsolutions.com</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top:14px; font-size:11px; color:#6b829e;">
              &copy;
              {{year}}
              Wynn Tax Solutions. All rights reserved.
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>